Title: Cobb Flexfit Pro-Formance COBB Cap - L/XL C-CO-Cap-Black-L-XL
Body (HTML):
Lightweight, serge polyspun fabric has the look and feel of wool. Mid-profile cap, 3 1/4' crown with six eyelets. PermacCurv PE visor with 8 rows of stitching, fused hard buckram front panels, hypoallergenic and moisture wicking ability, and superior drying with matching under-visor. This COBB cap features a 3-D COBB logo embroidered on the wearer's left side. Available in 2 sizes: S/M: 6 3/4' - 7 1/4' L/XL: 7 1/8' - 7 5/8'

  • Embroidered White 3-D COBB Logo
  • 6580 Flexfit Pro-Formance Cap
  • 97% Polyester / 3% Spandex
  • Fitted Stretch Fit Closure
  • Moisture Wicking, Dries Quickly, Circulates Air for Coolness
